#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/docker.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Variable              | Purpose                                                                              |\n"
"|-----------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| `APP_ENV`             | Application environment. `dev` enables developer-friendly behavior.                  |\n"
"| `APP_DEBUG`           | Enables detailed error output and debug panels.                                      |\n"
"| `SERVER_NAME`         | Caddy server address — `:80` means listen on all interfaces on port 80.              |\n"
"| `XDEBUG_MODE`         | Xdebug mode. Use `develop` for helpers and `debug` to enable step debugging.         |\n"
"| `COMPOSER_CACHE_DIR`  | Moves Composer's cache into the mounted volume so it persists between runs.          |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/docker.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "docker/test/.env"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/docker.md
